3. INSTALLING\par
\par
   FR2.54 includes full source code. Trial version contains almost all sources\par
(only one compiled unit FR_Class.dcu / FR_class.obj ). \par
! DON'T CHANGE ANYTHING IN FR.INC FILE OF TRIAL FR VERSION !\par
\par
3.1. Run fr254.exe and follow to instructions of installation program\par
\par
3.2. FastReport supports a significant number of languages.\par
\par
   FastReport has several language sets: English, German, French, Danish, \par
Portuguese-brazil, Spanish, Dutch, Swedish, Turkish, Italian, Polish, Czech, \par
Hungarian, Slovene, Catalon, Slovak, Russian, Chinese, Ukrainian. \par
   Resources are located in ..\\FR\\RES folder. By default, FastReport library \par
setups with English resources. To use German resources, copy the files with \par
RES-extensions from ..\\FR\\RES\\GERMAN folder to ..\\FR\\SOURCE folder and \par
recompile package (see more in setup.txt).\par
That way, you can make your application fully German, French etc\par
\par
   WARNING! The old datamanager (TfrDataStorage) is outdated. It included in\par
this FR version, but will be removed in the next version. We highly \par
recommended to stop using it, move to new components and convert your existing\par
reports.\par
\par
3.3. For recompile libraries see setup.txt\par
