4. BACKWARD COMPATIBILITY\par
   .frf files from FR2.1...FR2.54 is compatible. You can use FR2.1 .frf\par
in FR2.4; but you can't use new .frf files in older FR versions and builds.\par
   See faq.txt if you want to open FreeReport 2.21 files.\par
   FR CLX files can be opened by FR2.45 version and higher. \par
Since CLX and VCL uses different paper numbering you may need to change \par
paper format after opening FR CLX report file. \par
   Old datamanager (TfrDataManager) is not installed by default. Remove\par
comment from \{$DEFINE DATAMANAGER\} line in FR.inc file to install it.\par
